data.title: Norwegian Railway - NORWAY TRAINS
data.meta_description: Looking for a map of the Norwegian railway? Find all the information regarding the train system in Norway and book your tickets with Norway Trains!
data.text:
The length of Norwegian railway system is 4.087km. Out of it 2.662km is electrified and 64 km adapted for high-speed train travel. The biggest saturation of railway tracks is located in the south of the country.

Most popular operational Norwegian lines are:

Bergen

​Flam

Bratsberg

Dovre

Drammen

Gardermoen

​etc.

Operational museum railway lines:

Kroder

Setesdal

Urskog-Holand

Thamshavn

Rjukan

Valdres

etc.

*https://www.happyrail.com/uploads/landingpage_block_images/17sk011_scandinavie.jpg
